  <brief_title>Neoadjuvant Adriamycin and Ifosfamide Plus High-Dose ICE in Patients With Soft Tissue Sarcoma (STS)</brief_title>
  <official_title>Phase II Study of Neoadjuvant Dose-Intensive Chemotherapy With Adriamycin and Ifosfamide Followed by High-Dose ICE in Locally Advanced Soft Tissue Sarcomas</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>University Hospital Tuebingen</agency>
